AssumeRoleWithSAML.name: AssumeRoleWithSAML
AssumeRoleWithSAML.description:
Returns a set of temporary security credentials for users who have been authenticated
                                                via a SAML authentication response

AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity.name: AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity
AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity.description:
Returns a set of temporary security credentials for users who have been authenticated
                                                in a mobile or web application with a web identity provider

DecodeAuthorizationMessage.name: DecodeAuthorizationMessage
DecodeAuthorizationMessage.description:
Decodes additional information about the authorization status of a request from an
                                                encoded message returned in response to an AWS request

GetAccessKeyInfo.name: GetAccessKeyInfo
GetAccessKeyInfo.description: Returns details about the access key id passed as a parameter to the request.

GetCallerIdentity.name: GetCallerIdentity
GetCallerIdentity.description: Returns details about the IAM identity whose credentials are used to call the API

GetFederationToken.name: GetFederationToken
GetFederationToken.description:
Returns a set of temporary security credentials (consisting of an access key ID, a
                                                secret access key, and a security token) for a federated user

GetServiceBearerToken.name: GetServiceBearerToken
GetServiceBearerToken.description: Returns a STS bearer token for an AWS root user, IAM role, or an IAM user

GetSessionToken.name: GetSessionToken
GetSessionToken.description:
Returns a set of temporary security credentials (consisting of an access key ID, a
                                                secret access key, and a security token) for an AWS account or IAM user

TagSession.name: TagSession
TagSession.description: Grants permission to add tags to a STS session
